Lagos state – Some of the suspected thugs who attacked voters in Elegushi area of Lagos state have been paraded by soldiers. The suspected thugs were seen packed in a bus and were also begging for mercy from the security operatives when paraded, adding that they did nothing and have no gun. One of them disclosed that he is from “Elegushi family”. Watch the video below………… A post shared by Lindaikejiblog (@lindaikejiblogofficial)